WEBVTT

01:09:31.000 --> 01:09:35.999
What should we try for our next segment?

01:09:36.000 --> 01:09:38.999
Hyung, you're really fast at composing
and writing lyrics too.

01:09:39.000 --> 01:09:39.999
You're seriously quick.

01:09:40.000 --> 01:09:40.999
Right, right.

01:09:41.000 --> 01:09:42.999
Let's be honest—you are a genius.

01:09:43.000 --> 01:09:43.999
I'm not.

01:09:44.000 --> 01:09:44.999
What genius?

01:09:45.000 --> 01:09:45.999
How about our song...

01:09:46.000 --> 01:09:47.999
The chorus of “Wait for You.”

01:09:48.000 --> 01:09:49.999
[They quote the “Wait for You” chorus]

01:09:50.000 --> 01:09:50.999
[They repeat part of the chorus]

01:09:51.000 --> 01:09:56.999
What if we turn that part into a rap
and improvise it together right now?

01:09:57.000 --> 01:09:58.999
Yejun-hyung already did his homework.

01:09:59.000 --> 01:10:00.999
Then, together with Yejun-hyung...

01:10:01.000 --> 01:10:01.999
Yejun-hyung did the homework.

01:10:02.000 --> 01:10:02.999
You did the homework?

01:10:03.000 --> 01:10:03.999
Yes.

01:10:04.000 --> 01:10:04.999
You did?

01:10:05.000 --> 01:10:05.999
The producer gave me homework.

01:10:06.000 --> 01:10:06.999
Really?

01:10:07.000 --> 01:10:07.999
Let's hear it, then.

01:10:08.000 --> 01:10:11.999
I thought you could make something now.
I'll try too.

01:10:12.000 --> 01:10:13.999
I haven't heard it yet either.

01:10:14.000 --> 01:10:14.999
Wait a moment.

01:10:15.000 --> 01:10:15.999
I'll open the members' chat.

01:10:16.000 --> 01:10:16.999
Okay.

01:10:17.000 --> 01:10:18.999
I'm seriously in trouble now.

01:10:19.000 --> 01:10:19.999
I need to come up with something too.

01:10:20.000 --> 01:10:21.999
There are so many lyrics in the chat.

01:10:22.000 --> 01:10:23.999
Several versions, too.

01:10:24.000 --> 01:10:25.999
You kept them all, just in case.

01:10:26.000 --> 01:10:26.999
You really worked hard...

01:10:27.000 --> 01:10:28.999
Wait—the members' chat...

01:10:29.000 --> 01:10:30.999
Don't show it! Don't show it!

01:10:31.000 --> 01:10:32.999
This is bad. What am I going to do?

01:10:33.000 --> 01:10:37.999
You didn't just go,
‘I'll wait—gang, gang, gang,’ right?

01:10:38.000 --> 01:10:38.999
No.

01:10:39.000 --> 01:10:40.999
Could I practice once too?

01:10:41.000 --> 01:10:41.999
Sure. That sounds great.

01:10:42.000 --> 01:10:44.999
Whisper it—like this.

01:10:45.000 --> 01:10:46.999
Something like that.

01:10:47.000 --> 01:10:48.999
He really is in trouble.

01:10:49.000 --> 01:10:50.999
Wow, this...

01:10:51.000 --> 01:10:52.999
Hey, weren't we keeping this casual?

01:10:53.000 --> 01:10:54.999
We made the intro way too intense.

01:10:55.000 --> 01:10:57.999
[Yejun rehearses his “Wait for You” rap]

01:10:58.000 --> 01:11:00.999
[Yejun rehearses his “Wait for You” rap]

01:11:01.000 --> 01:11:02.999
[Yejun rehearses his “Wait for You” rap]

01:11:03.000 --> 01:11:05.999
[Yejun rehearses his “Wait for You” rap]

01:11:06.000 --> 01:11:07.999
[Yejun rehearses his “Wait for You” rap]

01:11:08.000 --> 01:11:09.999
[Yejun rehearses his “Wait for You” rap]

01:11:10.000 --> 01:11:10.999
So it fits...

01:11:11.000 --> 01:11:12.999
I'm working it out in my head.

01:11:13.000 --> 01:11:18.999
Practice, practice.

01:11:19.000 --> 01:11:20.999
Okay, I'll do it right away.

01:11:21.000 --> 01:11:25.999
Wow, I'm really in trouble. What do I do?

01:11:26.000 --> 01:11:27.999
You can do it.

01:11:28.000 --> 01:11:28.999
I'm seriously in trouble.

01:11:29.000 --> 01:11:33.999
This is when you say, ‘You can do it.’

01:11:34.000 --> 01:11:36.999
Wow, this song is seriously unfair.

01:11:37.000 --> 01:11:38.999
Stand or sit? We'll sit.

01:11:39.000 --> 01:11:39.999
Take your time and work. We'll sit.

01:11:40.000 --> 01:11:40.999
Nice homework!

01:11:41.000 --> 01:11:42.999
We'll just hang out. Take your time.

01:11:43.000 --> 01:11:43.999
Okay.

01:11:44.000 --> 01:11:46.999
What do I do? I'm actually sweating.

01:11:47.000 --> 01:11:48.999
Cute.

01:11:49.000 --> 01:11:50.999
Okay.

01:11:51.000 --> 01:11:54.999
[Yejun begins his “Wait for You” rap]

01:11:55.000 --> 01:11:57.999
[Yejun raps about waiting in the same place]

01:11:58.000 --> 01:11:59.999
[Yejun raps about seasons passing]

01:12:00.000 --> 01:12:02.999
[Yejun raps about thinking only of one person]

01:12:03.000 --> 01:12:04.999
[Yejun raps about going in circles]

01:12:05.000 --> 01:12:06.999
[Yejun continues his improvised verse]

01:12:07.000 --> 01:12:09.999
[Yejun raps about being stuck at the starting line]

01:12:10.000 --> 01:12:12.999
If I wait a little, you'll come back, right?

01:12:13.000 --> 01:12:14.999
If you have time, you'll call me, right?

01:12:15.000 --> 01:12:17.999
I'm the one who keeps waiting only for you.

01:12:18.000 --> 01:12:19.999
And who could that be?

01:12:20.000 --> 01:12:20.999
Nam Yejun!

01:12:21.000 --> 01:12:25.999
Wait a moment.

01:12:26.000 --> 01:12:27.999
Wait a moment.

01:12:28.000 --> 01:12:28.999
Hold on.

01:12:29.000 --> 01:12:30.999
I'll wait a little.

01:12:31.000 --> 01:12:32.999
So that was intentional, right?

01:12:33.000 --> 01:12:33.999
I'll wait a little, hyung.

01:12:34.000 --> 01:12:34.999
Hyung, I'm really sorry I laughed.

01:12:35.000 --> 01:12:36.999
I'll wait a little.

01:12:37.000 --> 01:12:40.999
I'm so sorry I laughed.
It wasn't because it was funny—

01:12:41.000 --> 01:12:42.999
Shall we wait a moment, everyone?

01:12:43.000 --> 01:12:45.999
I don't think hyung is ready yet.

01:12:46.000 --> 01:12:47.999
Don't cry.

01:12:48.000 --> 01:12:53.999
No, why...

01:12:54.000 --> 01:12:54.999
