01:12:55.000 --> 01:12:55.999
No, no—why? Why?

01:12:56.000 --> 01:12:58.999
It was good! Why?

01:12:59.000 --> 01:13:00.999
Why are you laughing?

01:13:01.000 --> 01:13:02.999
I wasn't laughing.

01:13:03.000 --> 01:13:04.999
I never laugh.

01:13:05.000 --> 01:13:06.999
I'll wait a little.

01:13:07.000 --> 01:13:09.999
If I wait a little, you'll come back, right?

01:13:10.000 --> 01:13:12.999
[Yejun falters during the rap]

01:13:13.000 --> 01:13:13.999
One more time.

01:13:14.000 --> 01:13:14.999
