01:13:15.000 --> 01:13:15.999
Please, just one more time.

01:13:16.000 --> 01:13:16.999
Seriously, please show us one more time.

01:13:17.000 --> 01:13:17.999
You're really mean, you know that?

01:13:18.000 --> 01:13:19.999
No, no, no. I won't laugh.

01:13:20.000 --> 01:13:21.999
Fans say the stream cut out earlier.

01:13:22.000 --> 01:13:22.999
Because it was so good.

01:13:23.000 --> 01:13:23.999
Okay, I'll go all the way through.

01:13:24.000 --> 01:13:24.999
Yes, yes.

01:13:25.000 --> 01:13:25.999
Go ahead, laugh some more.

01:13:26.000 --> 01:13:26.999
Ahhh...

01:13:27.000 --> 01:13:27.999
[Yejun begins the rap again]

01:13:28.000 --> 01:13:28.999
[Yejun raps his “Wait for You” verse]

01:13:29.000 --> 01:13:29.999
[Yejun raps about waiting]

01:13:30.000 --> 01:13:30.999
[Yejun raps about seasons passing]

01:13:31.000 --> 01:13:31.999
[Yejun raps about seeing only one person]

01:13:32.000 --> 01:13:32.999
[Yejun raps about going in circles]

01:13:33.000 --> 01:13:33.999
[They react during the rap]

01:13:34.000 --> 01:13:34.999
I mean...

01:13:35.000 --> 01:13:35.999
