01:13:36.000 --> 01:13:36.999
Wait a little—you'll come back, right?

01:13:37.000 --> 01:13:37.999
[Yejun repeats the setup to his punchline]

01:13:38.000 --> 01:13:38.999
Keep waiting—you'll come back, right?

01:13:39.000 --> 01:13:39.999
Keep waiting—you'll come back, right?

01:13:40.000 --> 01:13:40.999
Keep waiting—you'll come back, right?

01:13:41.000 --> 01:13:41.999
If you have time, you'll call me, right?

01:13:42.000 --> 01:13:42.999
I'm the one who only has eyes for you.

01:13:43.000 --> 01:13:43.999
And who could that be?

01:13:44.000 --> 01:13:44.999
Nam Yejun!

01:13:45.000 --> 01:13:45.999
Wait a little—you'll come back, right?

01:13:46.000 --> 01:13:46.999
If you have time, you'll call me, right?

01:13:47.000 --> 01:13:47.999
I'm the one who only has eyes for you.

01:13:48.000 --> 01:13:48.999
And who could that be?

01:13:49.000 --> 01:13:49.999
Nam Yejun!

01:13:50.000 --> 01:13:50.999
That's who!

01:13:51.000 --> 01:13:51.999
[Yejun ad-libs]

01:13:52.000 --> 01:14:01.999
[Yejun ad-libs]

01:14:02.000 --> 01:14:06.999
Nice!

01:14:07.000 --> 01:14:07.999
It's good. I really need to save this.

01:14:08.000 --> 01:14:08.999
Let's develop it. Develop it.

01:14:09.000 --> 01:14:09.999
It's good.

01:14:10.000 --> 01:14:10.999
[They discuss how the flow should continue]

01:14:11.000 --> 01:14:14.999
Don't do that. That makes it more painful for me.

01:14:15.000 --> 01:14:18.999
No, but I...

01:40:39.000 --> 01:40:41.999
So we just check, close the door if there's no ghost, and come back, right?

01:40:42.000 --> 01:40:42.999
Yeah.

01:40:43.000 --> 01:40:44.999
Oh, there it is.

01:40:45.000 --> 01:40:50.999
