01:43:00.000 --> 01:43:01.999
What do we do? What do we do?!

01:43:02.000 --> 01:43:03.999
We have to go somewhere else.

01:43:04.000 --> 01:43:05.999
Somewhere else.

01:43:06.000 --> 01:43:07.999
