01:43:20.000 --> 01:43:21.999
[Laughs]

01:43:22.000 --> 01:43:23.999
That scared me!

01:43:24.000 --> 01:43:25.999
Oh, that startled me!

01:43:26.000 --> 01:43:27.999
[Laughs]

01:43:28.000 --> 01:43:29.999
Oh...

01:43:30.000 --> 01:43:31.999
I need to turn the volume down.

01:43:32.000 --> 01:43:33.999
That startled me!

01:43:34.000 --> 01:43:35.999
[Laughs]

01:43:36.000 --> 01:43:37.999
Turn it down a little.

01:43:38.000 --> 01:43:39.999
