01:43:40.000 --> 01:43:41.999
[Laughs]

01:43:42.000 --> 01:43:43.999
[Laughs]

01:43:44.000 --> 01:43:45.999
Ah...

01:43:46.000 --> 01:43:47.999
Does anyone want to try?

01:43:48.000 --> 01:43:49.999
I'm too good at it—Eunho hyung, you try.

01:43:50.000 --> 01:43:51.999
I don't think I can do it.

01:43:52.000 --> 01:43:53.999
I think I just pulled a muscle.

01:43:54.000 --> 01:43:55.999
Are you okay?

01:43:56.000 --> 01:43:57.999
I'm okay.

01:43:58.000 --> 01:43:59.999
Ah, it loosened up.

01:44:00.000 --> 01:44:01.999
That quickly?

01:44:02.000 --> 01:44:03.999
Wow.

01:44:04.000 --> 01:44:05.999
So this...

01:44:06.000 --> 01:44:07.999
When the flashlight ghost comes in...

01:44:08.000 --> 01:44:09.999
we have to lure it with the flashlight?

01:44:10.000 --> 01:44:11.999
By shining it somewhere else?

01:44:12.000 --> 01:44:13.999
[Laughs]

01:44:14.000 --> 01:44:15.999
So we're not the ones who run away?

01:44:16.000 --> 01:44:17.999
Mm-hm.
